meta {
  name: By id config_recipe
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

get {
  url: {{host}}/api/config/{{bu_code}}/recipe/:id
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

headers {
  x-app-id: {{x_app_id}}
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get Recipe by ID
  ดึงข้อมูลสูตรอาหารเดียวตาม ID พร้อมรายการส่วนผสม ปริมาณ และขั้นตอนการเตรียม

  Retrieves a specific recipe with its full ingredient list, quantities, and preparation steps for menu costing and inventory tracking.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Recipe ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "code": "RCP-001",
      "name": "Tom Yum Kung",
      "description": "Spicy shrimp soup",
      "difficulty": "MEDIUM",
      "base_yield": 4,
      "base_yield_unit": "portion",
      "prep_time": 15,
      "cook_time": 20,
      "total_ingredient_cost": 120.00,
      "cost_per_portion": 30.00,
      "status": "DRAFT",
      "ingredients": [],
      "preparation_steps": [],
      "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Bearer token is missing or invalid |
  | 403 | User lacks recipe view permission |
  | 404 | Recipe not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

